Invoice Processing Policy

Only invoices with a total amount of $100,000 USD or less will be accepted.

Invoices older than 3 months from the date of receipt will not be processed.

All invoices must include:

Vendor name

Invoice number and date

Description of goods/services

Total amount and payment terms

Exceptions require written approval from the Finance Manager.

